Published Date: 2025-11-07. Closing Date: 2025-12-22. Competition: ICB. Financier Name: Self Financed

Summary: Contracting the Service for the Conduct of Cognitive, Emotional and Physical-Functional Stimulation Workshops for People with Cognitive Deterioration.. Description: Description of the service: The cognitive, emotional and physical-functional stimulation workshop for people with cognitive impairment is designed for people over 65 with memory impairments or other abilities, through the training of cognitive and physical-functional skills and with the stimulation of positive emotions. The activities will be planned in a group format, which will bring benefits in the field of socialization and communication. This workshop will be aimed at people who are in the initial stages of a neurocognitive disorder, such as dementia of the Alzheimer type, or have difficulties with memory or other abilities and want to improve their cognitive performance.. The Citizen Mediation Service is a municipal resource aimed at all citizens, entities and companies of Olesa de Montserrat in order to stimulate and encourage the parties involved to build, for themselves, a realistic and possible agreement for the resolution of certain conflicts born within the social structure. It is therefore a way complementary and/or alternative to traditional conflict resolution systems in the municipality of Olesa de Montserrat. The principles that must govern the Citizen Mediation Service are: the voluntariness of the parties when using it, the neutrality of the professionals who manage the service, the confidentiality of the process, respect for human dignity, proximity in the territory and the free service..
